THE FRAMEWORK FOR WORKING IS LARAVEL AND VUEJS AS DISCUSSED ON THE TALK WE HAD

I DID A PARENT - CHILD COMPONENT JUST TO SHOW HOW THEY WORK COMBINED

THE API ROUTES WERE SEPARETED FROM WEB ROUTES AS FRAMEWORK IS INTENDED TO BE

AS YOU CAN SPECIFY [N] NUMBER OF DESIRED BOMBS, WHEN THE BOARD IS CREATED IT WILL REDUCE THEM TO 90% OF THE 
TOTAL SQUARES AVAILABLE TO PLAY, THIS MEANS IN A 10 X 10 SETUP YOU CAN HAVE UP TO 90 BOMBS, THE IDEA BEHIMD
THIS IS TO MAKE THE GAME "PLAYABLE"


